{"tid":1321003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"師奶大鬧聖保祿醫院 求起底","createTime":"2019-07-15T14:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T06:37:25.000Z","uid":241444,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d7695ee7d71e4a6a53101a62e3734b0680b750b7","tid":1321003,"uid":241444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:14:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=7PfXr3iirfA&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7PfXr3iirfA%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cN8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=ea59a92e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=7PfXr3iirfA&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n全片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係現場一定笑到失控<br />\n就咁睇明明個阿妹似小學生<br />\n喺度9叫事主o靚仔你識啲乜<br />\n反而做家姐嘅乜都做唔到其實都幾慘<br />\n可惜你有個咁嘅老母系我就唔認啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係應該要為當時嘅病人平反一下<br />\n個C9真係好嘈，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺度話人騷擾最騷擾嗰個就係佢<br />\n真係好唔應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要睇吓佢邊間學校點解會教出個咁英明嘅學生<br />\n雖然家教都睇得出好撚威武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hgGwfSY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhgGwfSY.png&h=aa8a09b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLdeX6o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLdeX6o.png&h=c54770ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c067ae66be5b357405950ab40d59b79a75b83a8","tid":1321003,"uid":241444,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,